# Task Management

Use `tkr` commands for all task management. Never create ad-hoc todo files.

- Check `tkr next --plain` for your next task
- Use `tkr claim <id>` before starting work
- Include ticket ID in commits: `feat({{.Prefix}}-N): description`
- Use `tkr done <id>` when finished
